    "active_lock_reason": null,
    "body": "User A on a system has a spack instance in her home directory.  She installs a bunch of packages.  In the process of building the packages, temporary files are put in /tmp/spack-staging.  This directory is owned by user A with permissions drwx------.\n\nUser B on the same system also creates a spack instance in her home directory.  When she tries to install packages, spack attempts to write to create temporary files in /tmp/spack-staging which fails because this directory is owned by user A.\n",
